title: Second coronavirus death recorded in Tasmania
description: Tasmania records its second coronavirus death, an elderly man who was being cared for at the Royal Hobart Hospital.
content:
Updated 
March 31, 2020 09:34:54
Tasmania has recorded its second coronavirus death, an elderly man who was being cared for at the Royal Hobart Hospital.
